data.description: **Clay-Chalkville schools** Conveniently located right off of Sweeney Hollow Road, this spacious split-level beauty is ready to become yours. 3 bedroom/2 full bath with large level fenced back yard and large back deck. There is plenty of room in the kitchen with cabinets galore, a breakfast bar and an eat-in-kitchen area. Three steps will take you to all 3 bedrooms and one full updated bath. Have a king-sized bed? No problem, it's no match in this oversized primary bedroom. From the kitchen, you can go downstairs to a bottom level that features another remodeled full bath, laundry room, storage area and a 14'x23' room where you can let your imagination run wild. Fenced -level backyard. Very convenient to Publix, Sam's, Walmart, movie theatre, Chick-Fil-A and interstate.
